# This directory stores PRD (Product Requirements Document) files for Ralph Loop
#
# Usage:
#   bootstralph prd "description"    Create a new PRD
#   bootstralph prd --list           List all PRDs
#   bootstralph ralph                Run Ralph loop on a PRD
#   ./ralph.sh                       Run Ralph via shell script
#   ./ralph.sh afk 10                Run 10 iterations unattended
#
# PRD files are named: prd-{slug}.json
# Overview files are named: prd-{slug}.overview.md
# Progress is logged to: progress.txt
